function collectForm(dry=false){const data={};new FormData(form).forEach((v,k)=>{data[k]=data[k]?data[k]+'\n'+v:v});$$('input[type=checkbox]',form).forEach(i=>data[i.name]=i.checked);if(dry)data.dryRun=true;return data}
